                                        <td>Age Limit</td>
                                        <td>No age limit; anyone can take the TOEFL exam.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Educational Qualification</td>
                                        <td>Typically taken after completing high school or equivalent.</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Requirement for Students</td>
